[32m+[m[32mâ”‚  â”œâ”€â”€ Oracle System (Enhanced)                                   â”‚[m
[32m+[m[32mâ”‚  â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ oracle-aggregator-v2.clar (Enhanced)                   â”‚[m
